# Conventional Commits - Financial Dashboard
# <type>: <short description>
#
# Types: feat | fix | ui | perf | docs | refactor | chore
#
# feat: new feature
# fix: bug fix
# ui: UI/layout changes
# perf: performance improvement
# docs: documentation
# refactor: code restructure without behavior change
# chore: maintenance
#
# Example:
# feat: add CSV import wizard
# fix: resolve snapshot update issue
# ui: overhaul review page layout
# perf: optimize hashing pipeline
